{"tid":578199,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"赤貧者食垃圾　港素食者：屍肉致癌何不食素","createTime":"2018-03-02T11:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T12:55:44.000Z","uid":92983,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"36c77e211c4adb99266185556ed9ac5acbacf0c2","tid":578199,"uid":92983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:59:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180302/photo/bkn-20180302180645621-0302_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180302183425\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180302%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180302180645621-0302_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180302183425&h=cd3287d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全球有逾7.6億人處於極度貧窮，三餐不得溫飽。近日有外媒報道，菲律賓的赤貧者需以垃圾堆中的剩肉果腹，情況令人不忍卒睹。惟有推廣素食的社交專頁表示，「屍肉致癌，何不吃素」，旋即惹來網民怒轟。<br />\n<br />\n有外國媒體報道，菲律賓的貧民區流行一種叫「Pagpag」的「回收肉」，即是將從垃圾堆翻出的廚餘剩肉，經人手清洗及加工後，以熟食形式售出的「菜餚」。因價格低廉，故十分受當地貧民歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n社交專頁「香港素食」就報道發貼，表示<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「幾時都是吃素好」、「吃肉即是吃死屍」、「屍肉致癌」，更謂「何不吃素」</span></span>，認為「製造屍肉的成本遠高過種植純素」。<br />\n<br />\n貼文發出後，惹來網民怒轟，斥其毫無愛心︰「話啲赤貧人口食屍肉致癌，喂，你把口真係賤到一個點」。有人質疑「人地（哋）屍肉飯，一客賣0.2美金（約1.5港元），你話俾（畀）我知邊間純素餐廳有邊一道菜賣得平過2蚊港紙？」<br />\n<br />\n另有網民諷謂，該素食專頁的說法為「現代版何不食肉糜」，質疑他「素口不素心」。更有人直言，「簡直影衰正常的素食者」。<br />\n<br />\n面對猛烈批評，專頁終回應指，一直以來分享資訊，是希望大家能反思「吃素與吃肉的背後真相」。專頁指「吃肉無疑是吃進毒素」，認為當地人不能作選擇，但「我們有得選擇」，勸喻大家「考慮吃長素或每天減少吃肉」。<br />\n<br />\n該專頁又澄清指，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「小編沒有恥笑任何人，那是你閣下妄想」，並表示「高估了某些網民的理解能力」</span></span></strong>，最終對引起網民的曲解致歉。<br />\n<br />\n究竟是次風波是「觀點與角度」的問題，還是真相「越描越黑」？你又點睇呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180302/bkn-20180302180645621-0302_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180302%2Fbkn-20180302180645621-0302_00822_001.html&d=9PSWKmoeL2jtaxRuB1Z%2BeZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=0d07f1bb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180302/bkn-20180302180645621-0302_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"045ac4256ce26d35158a04affe3ee6d4002c39ea","tid":578199,"uid":166571,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:03:00.000Z","msg":"搞走素(膠)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/200250_ca7db32739c9304c7613ba75c27dea09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F200250_ca7db32739c9304c7613ba75c27dea09.jpg&h=3828eb95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"223344b169b48674a5e93a1b4ab45a4f94833b3f","tid":578199,"uid":92983,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"045ac4256ce26d35158a04affe3ee6d4002c39ea","tid":578199,"uid":166571,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:03:00.000Z","msg":"搞走素(膠)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/200250_ca7db32739c9304c7613ba75c27dea09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F200250_ca7db32739c9304c7613ba75c27dea09.jpg&h=3828eb95&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:03:52.000Z","msg":"素膠真係好可怕"},{"pid":"40fc6ab79bdc0dbc87dbcddc425a8e48a8e2414f","tid":578199,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:46:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pEguuASirDg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpEguuASirDg&d=9PSWKmoeL2jtaxRuB1Z%2BeZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=37013b9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pEguuASirDg</a>"},{"pid":"96ed2c8b92a23103567735f6a356f40508b3cff6","tid":578199,"uid":137912,"like"